reporting-org.narrative: New Zealand Ministry of Foreign Affairs and Trade

description.narrative: The design and delivery of the Foreign Service Training Programme (FSTP) to the Papua New Guinea (PNG) Department of Foreign Affairs (DFA) and other departments to build staff capacity in key areas (such as, communications, negotiations, trade and diplomatic craft) and promote consistency in foreign policy across the DFA and other PNG Government Departments. It also aims to improve trainee professionalism, command of English, and reflect PNG’s strengths and cultural diversity.
